{%- comment -%}
  Section: Vertex AI Home Recommendations (RFY / Trending)
  Placement: home_below_hero — below the hero banner slider, above category pills.

  Gated on model ACTIVE (~2026-05-07). Until then:
  - customer.metafields.vertex.recommended_for_you is nil (model TRAINING)
  - shop.metafields.vertex.trending is nil (not yet written by precompute)
  - The empty-state gate in vertex-recommendations.liquid suppresses the section
  So the section can be safely added to templates/index.json now; nothing renders.

  When model goes ACTIVE, precompute writes:
  - customer.metafields.vertex.recommended_for_you (per-customer, logged-in path)
  - shop.metafields.vertex.trending (global fallback, anonymous path)
  Both are JSON arrays of product references → same format as vertex.recs.

  Phase 1b-γ.9 (2026-05-07 estimated). See task-1-recommendations.md §Slot3,
  open questions 1 and 2, and the plan at ~/.claude/plans/woolly-humming-quokka.md.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  if customer
    assign rfy_title    = section.settings.title_logged_in    | default: 'Trending in your routine'
    assign rfy_subtitle = section.settings.subtitle_logged_in | default: ''
  else
    assign rfy_title    = section.settings.title_anon         | default: 'Trending now'
    assign rfy_subtitle = section.settings.subtitle_anon      | default: ''
  endif
-%}

{% render 'vertex-recommendations',
    placement: 'home_below_hero',
    customer: customer,
    title: rfy_title,
    subtitle: rfy_subtitle
%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Vertex recommendations",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title_logged_in",
      "label": "Title (logged-in customer)",
      "default": "Trending in your routine"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle_logged_in",
      "label": "Subtitle (logged-in customer)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title_anon",
      "label": "Title (anonymous visitor)",
      "default": "Trending now"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle_anon",
      "label": "Subtitle (anonymous visitor)"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Vertex recommendations",
      "category": "Recommendations"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
